sk.tsystems.forum.services

Class TopicServices

  • java.lang.Object
    • sk.tsystems.forum.services.TopicServices

  • public class TopicServices
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains methods needed for adding, removing and retrieving information about stored data of Topic class from the database.

    martinharcarik

      • addTopicToDatabase

        public void addTopicToDatabase(Topic topic)
        Adds the instance of Topic class into database. Instance of Topic is sent as a parameter.
        Parameters:
        topic - is the instance of class Topic that needs to be stored in database.

      • getTopicID

        public int getTopicID(java.lang.String topic)
        Gets the integer value of the property 'topicID' of the instance of the Topic class.
        Parameters:
        topic - represents value of 'topic' property of Topic class, used to select the needed instance of Topic class
        Returns:
        integer value of 'topicID' property of the instance of Topic class, or 0 if there is no instance of Topic class with specified 'topic' property stored in the database.

      • getPresentTopic

        public Topic getPresentTopic(java.lang.String topic)
        Gets the instance of Topic class. Method contains of getting id property of Topic class, then returning the found instance of Topic class.
        Parameters:
        topic - represents value of 'topic' property, needed to get 'topicID' property of Topic class, passed as a parameter of method getTopicID
        Returns:
        the instance of Topic class or null, if there is no instance of Topic class with this 'topic' property stored in the database

      • getTopic

        public Topic getTopic(int topicID)
        Gets the instance of the Topic class from the database identified by the value of the property 'topicID'.
        Parameters:
        topicID - is value of 'topicID' property of the Topic class
        Returns:
        the instance of Topic class with specified value of it's property 'topicID' or null, if the specified instance is not present in the database

      • removeTopic

        public void removeTopic(java.lang.String topicName)
        Removes the instance of the Topic class with specified property 'topic' from database
        Parameters:
        topicName - is value of 'topic' property of the Topic class

      • updateTopic

        public void updateTopic(java.lang.String origTopic,
                        java.lang.String newTopic,
                        java.lang.String newVisibility)
        Sets the properties 'topic' and 'visibility' of the specified instance of the Topic class and stores this instance into the database.
        Parameters:
        origTopic - value of the property 'topic' stored in the database, used to retrieve the instance of the Topic class from the database before updating it's properties
        newTopic - new value of the property 'topic' of the Topic class to be stored in the database
        newVisibility - new value of the property 'topic' of the Topic class to be stored in the database

      • setSubscriber

        public void setSubscriber(Topic topic,
                          User user)
        Adds the specified instance of User class into the 'user' property of the instance of Topic class.
        Parameters:
        topic - is the instance of the Topic class
        user - is the instance of the User class to be added as a property of this instance of the Topic class

      • removeSubscriber
